

{"id":2655,"date":"2023-04-18T17:10:55","date_gmt":"2023-04-18T10:10:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=2655"},"modified":"2023-07-20T14:47:52","modified_gmt":"2023-07-20T07:47:52","slug":"lan-dau-tap-gym-nen-tap-may-nao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/lan-dau-tap-gym-nen-tap-may-nao\/","title":{"rendered":"L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym n\u00ean t\u1eadp m\u00e1y n\u00e0o?"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em><strong>L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, m\u00e1y m\u00f3c v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y hoang mang nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng lo l\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, The New Gym \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c m\u00e1y t\u1eadp ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The New Gym: m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft v\u00e0 m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n. <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n.<\/span><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><u><strong>L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111i t\u1eadp Gym n\u00ean t\u1eadp m\u00e1y n\u00e0o?<\/strong><\/u><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><strong>M\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3748\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3748\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3748 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-chay-bo.jpg\" alt=\"L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-chay-bo.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-chay-bo-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-chay-bo-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-chay-bo-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-chay-bo-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-chay-bo-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3748\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tim m\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n \u0111i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1u, ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 hay ch\u1ea1y n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch b\u1eadt m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9: \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 khi m\u00e1y \u0111ang t\u1eaft. \u0110\u1ec3 b\u1eadt m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, nh\u1ea5n n\u00fat B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u (Start) n\u1eb1m \u1edf gi\u1eefa b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch t\u1eaft m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9: Nh\u1ea5n n\u00fat K\u1ebft th\u00fac (Stop) b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u00fat B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u0103ng t\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i d\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc xu\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e1y s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 t\u1eaft.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9: C\u00f3 hai n\u00fat \u1edf b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1ea5n c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eang: C\u00f3 hai n\u00fat \u1edf b\u00ean tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9. Nh\u1ea5n m\u0169i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ed1c v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u00a0L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Gi\u1eef l\u01b0ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 vai ngang.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u00ecn th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh nh\u00ecn xu\u1ed1ng ch\u00e2n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u00e1nh vung tay sang hai b\u00ean v\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00fang \u1edf b\u00ean h\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>V\u00ed d\u1ee5 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tim m\u1ea1ch tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u0110i b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 trong 10-30 ph\u00fat.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao: Mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9? H\u00e3y th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1c qu\u00e3ng v\u1edbi 70-80% t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1i \u0111a trong 20 gi\u00e2y. Ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c qu\u00e3ng 10-20 gi\u00e2y, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. L\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i 9 l\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><strong>M\u00e1y <span style=\"color: #009fc2;\">tr\u01b0\u1ee3t<\/span> tuy\u1ebft<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3744\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3744\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3744 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-truot-tuyet-2.jpg\" alt=\"L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-truot-tuyet-2.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-truot-tuyet-2-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-truot-tuyet-2-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-truot-tuyet-2-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-truot-tuyet-2-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-truot-tuyet-2-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3744\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tim m\u1ea1ch. N\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1ng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1ea5p nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ec3 l\u00ean m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n, h\u00e3y b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p trong khi gi\u1eef ch\u1eb7t tay c\u1ea7m b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1eef th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p kia. Sau khi c\u1ea3 hai ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 an to\u00e0n tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ec1u hai ch\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch b\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u1eaft m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft: Khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n sau khi \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u1eadp, h\u00e3y nh\u1ea5n n\u00fat B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u (Start) \u1edf gi\u1eefa b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1edf m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft: \u0110\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n, h\u00e3y \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf ph\u00eda b\u00ean tay ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n. Nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o m\u0169i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n v\u00e0 do \u0111\u00f3, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ed1c m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft: \u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1ea5n n\u00fat l\u00ean ho\u1eb7c xu\u1ed1ng \u1edf ph\u00eda b\u00ean tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n nh\u01b0 trong h\u00ecnh. Vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ed1c s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u00e0i t\u1eadp tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n v\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea1m vi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng tay v\u00e0 ch\u00e2n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o gi\u1eef th\u1eb3ng l\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh cong l\u01b0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">G\u1ed3ng ch\u1eb7t c\u01a1 b\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng tr\u00ean m\u00e1y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u00ecn th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft l\u00ean c\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u00e1nh c\u0103ng c\u01a1 vai &#8211; gi\u1eef cho ch\u00fang d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tim m\u1ea1ch tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh: R\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tim m\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tr\u00ean m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft trong 10-30 ph\u00fat,<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao: B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng nh\u1ecbp tim? H\u00e3y th\u1eed c\u00e1c qu\u00e3ng v\u1edbi 70-80% t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1i \u0111a trong 10 gi\u00e2y. Ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c qu\u00e3ng 10-20 gi\u00e2y, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. L\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i 9 l\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><strong>M\u00e1y ch\u00e8o <span style=\"color: #009fc2;\">thuy\u1ec1n<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3746\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3746\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3746 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-cheo-thuyen-2.jpg\" alt=\"L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-cheo-thuyen-2.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-cheo-thuyen-2-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-cheo-thuyen-2-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-cheo-thuyen-2-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-cheo-thuyen-2-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/may-cheo-thuyen-2-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3746\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i t\u1eadp to\u00e0n th\u00e2n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eb9. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, gi\u00fap r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh ph\u1ea7n th\u00e2n tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Gi\u1eef th\u1eb3ng l\u01b0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Gi\u1eef cho khu\u1ef7u tay c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">G\u1ed3ng ch\u1eb7t c\u01a1 b\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Gi\u1eef h\u01a1i th\u1edf \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tim m\u1ea1ch tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh: T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tim m\u1ea1ch c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00e1y \u1edf m\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n th\u1ea5p. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hay \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p l\u00ean c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao: B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed th\u00e1ch b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n? H\u00e3y th\u1eed ch\u00e8o 200m tr\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n trong kho\u1ea3ng 60-75% t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1i \u0111a. Ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c qu\u00e3ng trong 60 gi\u00e2y. L\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i 3 l\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o h\u1ea1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb t\u1eeb v\u00ec gh\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n n\u1eb1m \u1edf ph\u00eda b\u00ean tay ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n. The New Gym khuy\u00ean b\u1ea1n n\u00ean th\u1eed v\u1edbi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Kh\u00f3a ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bu\u1ed9c ch\u1eb7t v\u00e0o m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o n\u00fat Menu \u1edf g\u00f3c d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eadt m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e8o v\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eadt.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o n\u00fat menu \u1edf g\u00f3c d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng b\u00ean tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eadt m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e8o v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e8o s\u1ebd b\u1eadt.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1eafm l\u1ea5y thanh tay c\u1ea7m b\u1eb1ng hai tay v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ph\u1ea7n b\u00e0n tay.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Gi\u1eef th\u1eb3ng l\u01b0ng, du\u1ed7i th\u1eb3ng ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 ch\u00e8o tay c\u1ea7m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda sau b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch k\u00e9o c\u01a1 x\u00f4 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. H\u00e3y t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Sau \u0111\u00f3 du\u1ed7i th\u1eb3ng c\u00e1nh tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t b\u1ea1n. Khi tay c\u1ea7m qua \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, h\u00e3y u\u1ed1n cong \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 di chuy\u1ec3n m\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. L\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u00e2y gi\u1edd b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc m\u00e1y n\u00e0y, t\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1eed d\u00f9ng ch\u00fang trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3\u00a0<span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><a style=\"color: #009fc2;\" href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/cac-thiet-bi-tap-luyen\/\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\">thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/span><\/a>\u00a0<\/span>n\u00e0o The New Gym c\u00f3 trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1eebng ng\u1ea1i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap t\u1eeb hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n &#8211; h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f2n ch\u1ea7n ch\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ebfn\u00a0<span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><a style=\"color: #009fc2;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/thenewgymvietnam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The New Gym<\/a><\/span>\u00a0v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u00f4i n\u00e0o! Xem ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp Gym g\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"messageView\" class=\"message-view \" tabindex=\"21\">\n<div id=\"messageViewContainer\" class=\" message-view__scroll \">\n<div>\n<div id=\"messageViewScroll\" class=\"message-view__scroll__inner fadeInAndOut \">\n<div class=\"chat-item flx me\">\n<div class=\"chat-content flx flx-col flx-cell me\">\n<div id=\"bb_msg_id_1683793590289\" class=\"chat-message wrap-message rotate-container me -send-time -reaction\" data-node-type=\"bubble-message\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<div class=\"card me last-msg has-status card--text\" data-id=\"div_LastSentMsg_Text\">\n<div><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span class=\"text\">\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch gi\u00e1, g\u00f3i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i: <\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span class=\"text\">Fanpage: The New Gym <\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span class=\"text\">Email: <\/span><a class=\"text-is-email\" href=\"mailto:cskh@thenewgym.vn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">cskh@thenewgym.vn<\/a> <\/span><\/div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span class=\"text\">Hotline: <\/span><a class=\"text-is-phone-number\">1900636920<\/a><span class=\"text\">.<\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"chatInput\" class=\"chat-input darwin\">\n<div class=\"chat-input__content\">\n<div class=\"chat-input__content__input\">\n<div id=\"chatInputv2\" class=\"flx\">\n<div class=\"chat-input-container \">\n<div class=\"flx w100 \"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n,\u00a0S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n, C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n, t\u1eadp m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, t\u1eadp m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, t\u1eadp m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n, ch\u1ec9nh m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, ch\u1ec9nh m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, ch\u1ec9nh m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft, m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n Trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, m\u00e1y m\u00f3c v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y hoang mang nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng lo l\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ph\u00f2ng [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":4878,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,9],"tags":[107,117,118,119],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2655"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2655"}],"version-history":[{"count":34,"href":"htt